Refund Policy

Overview

At **Shrinee**, your satisfaction is our priority. If you are not completely happy with your purchase, you may be eligible for a refund in accordance with the conditions outlined below.

---

Eligibility for Refunds

1. Refund requests must be made within **30 days of purchase**.
2. Jewellery must be **unused, unworn, and in its original condition**.
3. All **original packaging, certificates, and invoices** must be returned along with the item.
4. **Custom-made, personalized, or engraved items are not eligible** for refunds.
5. Items showing signs of wear, damage, or alteration will not qualify.
6. **A video recording of the unboxing/return packaging process is mandatory** to claim a refund.

---

Refund Process

1. To request a refund, contact our support team at **[support.shrinee@gmail.com](mailto:support.shrinee@gmail.com)** within the eligible period.
2. Our team will provide the return address and instructions.
3. Once the returned item is received, it will undergo a **quality inspection**.
4. If approved, refunds will be initiated within **7â€“10 business days**.

---

Mode of Refund

1. Refunds will be issued only to the **original payment method** used at the time of purchase.
2. For COD (Cash on Delivery) orders, refunds will be processed via **bank transfer/UPI**, and customers will need to share valid account details.
3. **Shipping and COD charges are non-refundable.**

---

Refunds for Damaged or Defective Items

1. If you receive a damaged, defective, or incorrect item, please notify us within **7 days of delivery**.
2. A **clear unboxing video is mandatory** to validate such claims.
3. Upon verification, you may choose between a **full refund or replacement**.

---

Non-Refundable Cases

* Custom or engraved items.
* Items purchased during **sale/discounted events** (unless defective).
* Returns made without prior approval.
* Items without original packaging, certificates, or invoices.

---

